Sentencas: Solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) has the potential to convert biomass to electrical power cleanly and efficiently by integrating with in situ gasification of biomass.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cell using agroforestry waste as fuel: A balance between power output and fuel utilization

Sentencas: It is necessary to keep a balance between maximizing the power output of fuel cells and minimizing the pretreatment of biomass.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cell using agroforestry waste as fuel: A balance between power output and fuel utilization

Sentencas: Herein, we report the comparison of output performance between the apple tree branches (ATB) dried at 110 degrees C and the one pyrolyzed at 500 degrees C in SOFCs.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cell using agroforestry waste as fuel: A balance between power output and fuel utilization

Sentencas: The results show that the peak power densities (PPD) of SOFCs operated at 850 degrees C were 157 and 238 mW cm(-2) for the dried and the pyrolyzed samples, respectively.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cell using agroforestry waste as fuel: A balance between power output and fuel utilization

Sentencas: And the corresponding apparent fuel utilizations for them were 18.1% and 24.6%, respectively.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cell using agroforestry waste as fuel: A balance between power output and fuel utilization

Sentencas: However, if counting the pyrolysis yield (similar to 28 wt%), the overall fuel utilization of the pyrolyzed sample declined from 24.6% to similar to 6.9%.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cell using agroforestry waste as fuel: A balance between power output and fuel utilization

Sentencas: In addition, if loading the steel slag (SS)-based catalyst catalyst to the dried sample, its PPD at 850 degrees C were almost doubled to 303 mW cm(-2), but the fuel utilization reduced to 9.2%.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cell using agroforestry waste as fuel: A balance between power output and fuel utilization

Sentencas: Meanwhile, SOFCs using the medium-density fiberboard (MDF) as fuel exhibited the parallel trends in electrochemical performance and fuel utilization.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cell using agroforestry waste as fuel: A balance between power output and fuel utilization
